# Ignore result files by default, then allow the curated result structure.
*
!.gitignore
!README.md
!README_CN.md

!basic_experiments/
!basic_experiments/**
!advanced_experiments/
!advanced_experiments/**

# Keep lightweight, reviewable result records and summaries.
!**/result.json
!**/summary.csv
!**/summary.json
!**/*_summary.csv
!**/*_summary.json
!**/*_summaries.csv
!**/*_stats.json
!**/stats.json
!**/*.md
!**/*.tex
!**/*.py
!**/*.sh

# Keep the local directory layout usable without committing heavy artifacts.
**/.DS_Store
**/agent_log.txt
**/config.json
**/comparison_snapshot.json
**/artifacts/
**/traj/
**/*.traj
**/*.xyz
**/*.pkl
**/*.yaml
**/*.txt
**/*.png
**/*.svg
**/*.pdf
**/*.zip
